Package kuusisto.simpool

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    Poolable
    The Poolable interface facilitates generic pooling and maintenance of valid internal state of pooled objects.
    PoolableFactory<T extends Poolable>
    The PoolableFactory interface facilitates creation of Poolable objects for Simpool.
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    Pool<T extends Poolable>
    The Pool class is used for the actual pooling of Poolable objects.
  • Exception Summary 
    Exception Description
    SimpoolException
    The SimpoolException class is the basic exception used by Simpool.
